JetV studied the maps intently.  Looking up at the size of the bot, 
he quinted, looking up in deep thought.  "Yea, well last report is 
that the Maximal Base is about here, on the tip of Africa.  Now by 
your size the best accessibilty will be this route here. " he sais as 
he pulles his finger along a path on the map, a yellow glowing line 
following it.  "There shouldn't be any other patrols of enemy bases 
and it should be a pretty uneventful trip.  I can't see any 
disturbances that could happen." he sais as he prepares a 
console.  "If you want to plug into this I can download a 
navigational system into your cerebro.  Should help you get there."
